ility twice and then cannot use this ability again until you finish a short or long rest. When firing an arrow from this weapon, you can declare an oracle shot, allowing you to project your sight through the arrow you fire for up to 10 minutes. You cannot use this ability again until you finish a short or long rest. When a creature is killed by an arrow from this weapon, a single 6-ft tree rapidly grows out of their corpse over the next minute.|PREVAREQ:Attunement_Fenthras,4	BONUS:WEAPON|TOHIT,DAMAGE|1|PREVARGTEQ:Attunement_Fenthras,2	BONUS:WEAPON|TOHIT,DAMAGE|1|PREVARGTEQ:Attunement_Fenthras,3	BONUS:WEAPON|TOHIT,DAMAGE|1|PREVARGTEQ:Attunement_Fenthras,4									
